Dear Officers of <%= @request.organization %>,

This email is to inform you that your <%= @request %> has been started, but requires further action before it will be considered submitted.

You may make changes to the request here <<%= request_items_url(@request) %>>.

When the request is ready for submission, any of the following may approve it here <<%= new_polymorphic_url([@request, 'approval']) %>>:

<% @request.users.required_for_status('completed').each do |user| -%>
 * <%= user.name %>
<% end -%>

<% if @request.basis.submissions_due_at && @request.basis.submissions_due_at > DateTime.now -%>
The next deadline for submissions is <%= @request.basis.submissions_due_at.to_s :us_ordinal %>.
<% end -%>

<% if @request.basis.contact_web -%>
More information is available here <<%= @request.basis.contact_web %>>.
<% end -%>

Sincerely,

<%= @request.basis.contact_name %>

